izers/\">Appetizers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/breakfast/\">Breakfast</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/homemade/\">Homemade Ingredients</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/drinks/\">Drinks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/jam-and-jelly/\">Jams and Jellies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/side-dishes/\">Side Dishes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/entrees/\">Entrees</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/soups/\">Soups</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/pasta/\">Pasta</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/pizza/\">Pizza</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/bread/\">Breads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/desserts/\">Desserts</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/subscribe/\">Subscribe</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"search\">\n<form action=\"/search/\" method=\"get\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"q\" id=\"q\" required=\"required\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" class=\"btn primary\" value=\"Search\"/>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"background\">\n<div class=\"fader\"></div>\n<img src=\"/recipes/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal_large.jpg\" alt=\"Raisin and Spice Oatmeal\" />\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\" itemscope itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Recipe\">\n<h1 itemprop=\"name\">Raisin and Spice Oatmeal</h1>\n<div class=\"socialButtons\">\n<div class=\"fb-like\" data-send=\"false\" data-href=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal/\" data-layout=\"button_count\" data-width=\"105\" data-show-faces=\"false\" data-action=\"like\"></div>\n<div class=\"pinterest\">\n<a href=\"http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com%2Frecipes%2Fraisin-and-spice-oatmeal%2F&media=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.makebetterfood.com/recipes/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal_large.jpg&description=Raisin%20and%20Spice%20Oatmeal\" class=\"pin-it-button\" count-layout=\"horizontal\">Pin It</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"print\"><a href=\"/pdfs/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Raisin and Spice Oatmeal');\"><img src=\"/img/icons/print.png\" alt=\"Print\" /></a><a href=\"/pdfs/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal.pdf\" onclick=\"logPrintEvent('Raisin and Spice Oatmeal');\">Print or download (PDF)</a></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\">\n<li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/\">Recipes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recipes/breakfast/\"><span itemprop=\"recipeCategory\">Breakfast</span></a></li>\n<li>Raisin and Spice Oatmeal</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"article\"><p>I remember when I was six years old, my mother would let me make my own breakfast by handing me a packet of Quaker Oats Raisin and Spice Instant Oatmeal. I'd carefully rip open the packet, pour it into my plastic bowl, and add just the right amount of water to make sure that it would be mushy but not too soupy. Microwave it for a minute or two and presto chango, breakfast was made!</p></div>\n<div itemprop=\"description\" class=\"description\">Instant oatmeal is like magic to a kid, but now that I've grown up, my favorite flavor doesn't taste so magical any more. That is, until now. This copy-cat recipes yields an instant oatmeal mix that cooks up in two minutes in the microwave without any nasty chemicals or preservatives. A magician doesn't give away his secrets, but this oatmeal is too delicious for me not to share. You can easily double or triple the ingredients to make extra dry mix for a yummy, healthy breakfast that you can prepare faster than you can say 'Abracadabra!'</div>\n<div class=\"stats\">\n<ul>\n<li>Prep: <meta itemprop=\"prepTime\" value=\"PT10M\"/>10 min</li>\n<li>Cook: <meta itemprop=\"cookTime\" value=\"PT2M\"/>2 min</li>\n<li>Total: <meta itemprop=\"totalTime\" value=\"PT12M\"/>12 min</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeYield\">Yields 5 to 6 servings</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"steps\">\n<div class=\"right\">\n<a href=\"/recipes/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal_large.jpg\"><img class=\"polaroid\" src=\"/recipes/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal.jpg\" alt=\"Raisin and Spice Oatmeal\" itemprop=\"image\"/></a>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"subheader\">Dry Mix</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">3 &frac34; cups quick oats</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 cup raisins</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac12; cup brown sugar</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac12; tablespoon ground cinnamon</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">1 teaspoon salt</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac14; teaspoon ground nutmeg</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac14; teaspoon all spice</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Mix all ingredients together in a large bowl. Transfer to an airtight container or zip lock storage bags. Label and store in a cool place. Mix will keep for six months if airtight.</li>\n<li class=\"subheader\">Cooking</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac34; cup raisin and spice dry oatmeal mix</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Pour mix in a microwave safe bowl.</li>\n<li class=\"ingredient\">&frac34; cup milk or water</li>\n<li class=\"direction\">Add milk or water to bowl and stir gently to combine. Microwave on high until cooked, about 2 minutes. Remove and stir, adding more milk or water as necessary to reach your desired consistency.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"footnote\">\n<div class=\"logo\">MakeBetterFood.com</div>\nFrom MakeBetterFood.com. <time itemprop=\"datePublished\" datetime=\"2013-03-14\">Mar 14, 2013</time>. (http://makebetterfood.com/recipes/raisin-and-spice-oatmeal/).\n</div>\n<!-- Microformat Ingredients -->\n<ul class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">3 &frac34; cups quick oats</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 cup raisins</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac12; cup brown sugar</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac12; tablespoon ground cinnamon</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">1 teaspoon salt</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac14; teaspoon ground nutmeg</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac14; teaspoon all spice</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac34; cup raisin and spice dry oatmeal mix</li>\n<li itemprop=\"ingredients\">&frac34; cup milk or water</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Microformat Steps -->\n<ol class=\"hidden\">\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Mix all ingredients together in a large bowl. Transfer to an airtight container or zip lock storage bags. Label and store in a cool place. Mix will keep for six months if airtight.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Pour mix in a microwave safe bowl.</li>\n<li itemprop=\"recipeInstructions\">Add milk or water to bowl and stir gently to combine. Microwave on high until cooked, about 2 minutes. Remove and stir, adding more milk or water as necessary to reach your desired consistency.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"notPrinted\">\n<div class=\"grid_12\">\n<div class=\"recipe\">\n<div class=\"grid_2 alpha\">\n<img src=\"/img/cookbook/cover_bestof_grid3.png\" alt=\"Best of Make Better Food\" border=\"0\" style=\"max-width: 138px; width:100%;\" class=\"dropShadow\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid_10 omega\">\n<h4>Get New Recipes via Email + Free Cookbook</h4>\n<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->\n<form action=\"http://makebetterfood.us5.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=23bb9cd41955f33d8db8c9e91&amp;id=f2cac69129\" method=\"post\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" name=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" class=\"validate clear pushTop10\" target=\"_blank\">\n<div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-error-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-success-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<input type=\"email\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"email\" name=\"EMAIL\" class=\"xlarge\" id=\"mce-EMAIL\" size=\"30\" onclick=\"clearEmail(this);\" onfocus=\"clearEmail(this);\" onblur=\"fillEmail(this);\" style=\"color: #222;\" required=\"required\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" class=\"btn primary\" name=\"subscribe\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe\" value=\"Subscribe and Get Your Free Cookbook\">\n</form>\n<!--End mc_embed_signup-->\n<p>Sign up to get free MakeBetterFood.com recipe